
extends ../layout

block variables
  - var pageID = 'help-subscription'
  - var pageTitle = 'To Subscrible to arXiv Eprints'

block main
  article.ui-container-fluid.ui-mobile-expand
    include navigation
    .ui-grid-80.ui-offset-10.ui-mobile-expand
      section
        h4.ui-header-compact To Subscrible to arXiv Eprints
        div
          p In the 
            strong "Preferences"
            |  page of your account, you can configure eprint subscriptions:
          ul
            li
              strong Categories: 
              |  Specifies the categories of eprints classified by arXiv.org. This field is not allowed to be left as blank.
            li
              strong Subjects:
              |  Refers to codes for the 
              a(href='http://www.aip.org/pacs' rel='external' target='_blank')
                abbr(title='Physics and Astronomy Classification Scheme') PACS
              | , the 
              a(href='http://www.ams.org/mathscinet/msc/pdfs/classifications2010.pdf' rel='external' target='_blank')
                abbr(title='Mathematics Subject Classification') MSC-class
              | , the 
              a(href='http://www.acm.org/about/class/ccs98-html' rel='external' target='_blank')
                abbr(title='ACM Computing Classification System') ACM-class
              | , or the 
              a(href='https://www.aeaweb.org/jel/guide/jel.php' rel='external' target='_blank')
                abbr(title=' Journal of Economic Literature Classification System') JEL-class
              | . However, these codes are not specified for all eprints.
            li
              strong Themes:
              |  Specifies the themes of eprints in the form 
              code category: topic
              | . Topics are sub-classifications of categories.
            li
              strong Keywords:
              |  Specifies the keywords of eprints which are extracted from the title and abstact or added by users.
            li
              strong Tags:
              |  Specifies the tags of eprints classified in a non-hierarchical manner.
            li
              strong Authors:
              |  Specifies the authors of eprints. For Latin characters like 
              code &aacute;
              | , 
              code &ntilde;
              | , and 
              code &ouml;
              | , you should remove their diacritics.
          p Then your subscriptions will appear in the 
            code /browse
            |  page, where you can also change filters temporarily.
